<p>Tech: Python+Flask+Pandas+Clickhouse+MySQL+Redis+Nginx+Docker</p>

<p><img src="/cicihou/assets/img/yidrone.png" /></p>

<p>Official Introduction Link: <a href="https://www.yimian.io/yidrone">click here</a></p>

<p>A monthly-refreshed, realtime-interactive e-commerce market viewing tool. Like a drone, it scouts categories and subcategories, brands, stores, and SKUs. It uses AI to automatically identify sub-segments by multiple attributes. It helps clients discover new market trends and scan competitive landscapes.</p>

<p>Capabilities</p>

<p>Use consumer spending data to uncover secrets behind top sellers, capture market trends, and gain insights into categories and brands</p>

